metadata.name: T R A N C E
metadata.description:
hypnotic, monotonous
an uninterrupted dance
of Light and Shadow 
their constant ebb and flow 
of Ying and Yang 
the timeless cycle
of Day and Night
a perpetual journey 
into the depths 
of our own minds
lost in the moment
savoring every second
until we are snapped back
to reality
.
3000 X 4000
